{"type":"article","id":13237,"title":"（轉發）日本捐陸100萬枚口罩防疫？企業出面打臉了","uid":27547,"topics":[1382,5419,5767],"contents":"日本捐陸100萬枚口罩防疫？企業出面打臉了<br>\nEBC 東森新聞<br>\n<br>\n發布時間&nbsp;: 2020年1月28日11:00<br>\n<br>\nLINE&nbsp;facebook&nbsp;KEEP&nbsp;COPY<br>\n<br>\nText Size&nbsp;391&nbsp;<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/article/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%8D%90%E9%99%B8100%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%9A%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%EF%BC%9F%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%87%BA%E9%9D%A2%E6%89%93%E8%87%89%E4%BA%86-QGnZQr/?utm_source=nt&amp;_fstview=1#\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">443</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hWtoyhzJyCFtSACAT9mB3DGhWCzRhbBtYNjZZWBFuVm8rMxhdZmRBNXEIUj57ME8FPDVPNXUJE2osNxxYb2VB/w644\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hWtoyhzJyCFtSACAT9mB3DGhWCzRhbBtYNjZZWBFuVm8rMxhdZmRBNXEIUj57ME8FPDVPNXUJE2osNxxYb2VB/w644\" alt=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hWtoyhzJyCFtSACAT9mB3DGhWCzRhbBtYNjZZWBFuVm8rMxhdZmRBNXEIUj57ME8FPDVPNXUJE2osNxxYb2VB/w644\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>See detail</center><br>\n<br>\n武漢肺炎疫情持續延燒，台灣目前已有5例確診病例，行政院長蘇貞昌日前下令口罩暫停出口1個月，卻惹來批評。而近日傳出有日本企業捐贈100萬副口罩給大陸防疫，引發網友討論，不過現在當事者卻出面打臉了。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n大陸媒體《<a href=\"http://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002YYAgMaH782cbqzY2i--S2MemXnilQovloTj7b0jDVgkU__\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鳳凰新聞</a>》26日報導，日本伊藤洋華堂緊急「捐贈」500 箱、共計80萬枚口罩給成都市，應對此次新型冠狀病毒疫情，口罩分別於24日和25日兩次航班分別到達成都雙流國際機場，甚至央視也在微博發文，指出該日本企業捐助的100萬枚口罩正在送往武漢的路途中。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n▼網路瘋傳日本企業捐贈大陸80萬枚口罩。（圖／翻攝自<a href=\"http://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002YYAgMaH782cbqzY2i--S2MemXnilQovloTj7b0jDVgkU__\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鳳凰新聞</a>）<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hhUvmgT7JN3pLFB8y73RILXFCNBV4eCR5LyJmeQh6aU4yJyd8f3B-FGgcOU1kJHAkJSFwFGwWLEs1IyN5dnF-/w644\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hhUvmgT7JN3pLFB8y73RILXFCNBV4eCR5LyJmeQh6aU4yJyd8f3B-FGgcOU1kJHAkJSFwFGwWLEs1IyN5dnF-/w644\" alt=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hhUvmgT7JN3pLFB8y73RILXFCNBV4eCR5LyJmeQh6aU4yJyd8f3B-FGgcOU1kJHAkJSFwFGwWLEs1IyN5dnF-/w644\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>See detail</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n▼央視微博發文指日本企業捐助的100萬副口罩正在送往武漢。（圖／翻攝自央視微博）<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h7pRtuK3baF9vDUAXy20XCFVbazBcYXtcCzs5XCxjNmsWPnhZW2khMUxfNzxHPS8BATgvMUgMc24ROnxcUmgh/w644\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h7pRtuK3baF9vDUAXy20XCFVbazBcYXtcCzs5XCxjNmsWPnhZW2khMUxfNzxHPS8BATgvMUgMc24ROnxcUmgh/w644\" alt=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h7pRtuK3baF9vDUAXy20XCFVbazBcYXtcCzs5XCxjNmsWPnhZW2khMUxfNzxHPS8BATgvMUgMc24ROnxcUmgh/w644\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>See detail</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n不過，根據日本媒體《<a href=\"https://rocketnews24.com/2020/01/27/1326497/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Rocketnews24</a>》27日報導，該當事的企業「伊藤洋華堂」事後出面接受訪問時表示，確實是有寄送80萬副口罩至大陸，但也強調當時是應「成都的要求，寄送口罩，根本沒有談論捐贈」，也就是說這些口罩全是陸方自己掏腰包購買的，而非捐贈。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n▼日本媒體報導，當事企業出面打臉了。（圖／翻攝自<a href=\"http://ishare.ifeng.com/c/s/v002YYAgMaH782cbqzY2i--S2MemXnilQovloTj7b0jDVgkU__\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">鳳凰新聞</a>）<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hxAler2SeJ25RHA8m9XxYOWtKJAFicDRtNSp2bRJyeVooLzdoZXhuAHJMLl57JWAwPylgAHEdPF8vKzNtbHlu/w644\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hxAler2SeJ25RHA8m9XxYOWtKJAFicDRtNSp2bRJyeVooLzdoZXhuAHJMLl57JWAwPylgAHEdPF8vKzNtbHlu/w644\" alt=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hxAler2SeJ25RHA8m9XxYOWtKJAFicDRtNSp2bRJyeVooLzdoZXhuAHJMLl57JWAwPylgAHEdPF8vKzNtbHlu/w644\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<center>See detail</center><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n網路上流出「謝謝日本捐贈的口罩」的傳聞，臉書粉專「<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/magician.mil/posts/179801886731637?__xts__%5b0%5d=68.ARDlpyVnPTsqQ42uPn_XkLLhW-66QinTnprOi849VxtKUVwhvKoyeiV_0Hb4X2RyjxTyy_SnN3MWMSKMIGtaPl-LWptPe0Kuk9jKeiqd6EMXJDC7Ii0adYtq6_Ke2OBmrxKcKqFqVCKBLIEUj4fLGsg3uyjRKbP2B9IyYc8ZfHtspynp8F8EVxDFVtAae0-aiWBsCUXI4m4Tgf5ZoXpo4CYG0yPutWVXQzbdJOi-7gCw5yb-zMaBrzYU6ZA9VdYjd3bAbO1VWYQavC0U0PmNUIAzmnxQj1xahJI93NKj8VQRJJlg8-vRg5Zm1Fxvw2IYHuhg6L3i6Fmoer81aZUUCMk&amp;__tn__=-R\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">屢敗の魔術師</a>」也貼出日本媒體的報導，掀起網友熱烈討論，紛紛留言說道「感謝贈與就不用給錢！真是好算計」、「日本企業傻眼！原來這口罩錢拿不到」、「可能想不付錢了」、「這樣做新聞！根本針對衝衝衝」。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n（封面為示意圖／東森新聞）<br>\n拼命捧日本的小粉紅心不知多碎，日本廠商表示誰說送的請不要強行公益","date":"2020-01-29","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}